      • initialize

        public Boolean initialize()
                   throws SQLConnectException,
                          SQLTimeoutException
        Initializes the process of loading data. This includes selecting to the correct database, and generating database if not existed.

        This method no longer generates tables due to now using the SQLObjectConverter API for loading and saving.

        Returns:
        Whether loading is required. Null for not required, true for loading using the load() method, and false for loading using the #loadFromOld() method.
        Throws:
        SQLConnectException - See SQLConnectException.
        SQLTimeoutException - See SQLTimeoutException.
